Sentencas: The effect of strontium content on microstructure in (LaxSr1-x)FeO3 (LSFO) ceramics was investigated.
Titulo: Effect of strontium content on microstructure in (LaxSr1-x)FeO3 ceramics

Sentencas: It was observed that grain size increased as strontium content increased: mean grain sizes of 2.4 mum for 60% strontium content and 6.1 mum for 80% strontium content were observed in LSFO ceramics after 1250degreesC/4 h sintering.
Titulo: Effect of strontium content on microstructure in (LaxSr1-x)FeO3 ceramics
